cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper deals with the problem of face verification using MeshFace photos, which is a computer vision problem. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel feature-oriented blind face inpainting framework, which involves deep learning techniques. This suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves image processing and manipulation, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
